data.description: BEAUTIFUL MOVE IN READY RANCHER on 3+ acres! Enjoy the peace and serenity of Country Living in this 3 bedroom 2 full bath home. As you enter, you flow through the spacious foyer into the open dining area and kitchen equipped with stainless steel appliances, ample cabinet space, and a butcher block island with bar stool seating. Off the kitchen, you have two great spaces to entertain or relax, the bright and roomy living room plus the huge  family room with new LVP flooring! Down the hall, you will find 3 generously sized bedrooms including the primary bedroom featuring a private ensuite bath. Enjoy the outdoors while relaxing on the expansive deck or sitting around the soothing fire pit. This home also features a workshop, detached shed, recently remodeled full bathroom, new roof, new well pump (2021) plus more! Come take a tour today to see all this home has to offer!
